      </article>
      <article class="icon-card sc-animate" data-animate="fade-up" data-delay="200">
        <div class="testimonial-stars">⭐⭐⭐⭐⭐</div>
        <p>"As an admin, changing product SEO and details instantly updates the live storefront."</p>
        <strong>- Store Manager</strong>
      </article>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>



<%- include('partials/footer') %>
